---
layout: default
---
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-screen-lg xl:max-w-screen-xl mx-auto p-8">
  <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl leading-none font-extrabold tracking-tight mt-10 mb-8 sm:mt-14 sm:mb-10">
    Welcome to my personal website, a place where I share <span class="txt-type" data-wait="3000" data-words='["Ideas", "Projects", "About Me"]'></span>
  </h1>

  <p class="max-w-screen-lg text-lg sm:text-2xl sm:leading-10 font-medium mb-10 sm:mb-11">A personal website made with <a href="#" class="font-mono text-info link font-bold">jekyll</a> static site generator, <a href="#" class="font-mono text-info link font-bold">tailwindcss framework</a>, <a href="#" class="font-mono text-info link font-bold">daisyUI</a> Tailwind CSS component library, and <a href="#" class="font-mono text-info link font-bold">tora moka</a> coffee.
  </p>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4 text-center">
    <button class="w-full sm:w-auto flex-none btn-primary btn hover:bg-primary-700 text-lg leading-6 font-semibold py-3 px-6 border border-transparent rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-white focus:ring-gray-900 focus:outline-none transition-colors duration-200">Get started</button>
  </div>

</div>

	<div class="py-16 sm:text-center">
		<h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl sm:text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold">Project</h1>
	</div>
<div class="relative sm:columns-1 md:columns-2 lg:columns-3 xl:columns-4 gap-8">
{% for pr in site.data.project %}
<div class="card border-solid border-2 border-sky-200 border-x-indigo-500 m-5 bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
  <figure><img src="https://opengraph.githubassets.com/a61c54682a835cb4ed3faf90dc671065ac00d04902dd3e3c50a8beb7aef3b307/{{ pr.img }}" alt="Image {{ pr.title }}" /></figure>
  <div class="card-body">
    <h2 class="card-title">
      {{ pr.title }}
      {% if pr.new == true %}
      <div class="badge badge-secondary">NEW</div>
      {% endif %}
    </h2>
    <p>
      {% for lang in pr.lang %}
      <span class="badge badge-outline">{{ lang }}</span>
      {% endfor %}
      </p>
    <p>{{ pr.desc }}</p>
    <div class="card-actions justify-end">
    	<a href="{{ pr.link | relative_url }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm btn-outline">View More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endfor %}
</div>
<div class="max-w-[52rem] mx-auto px-4 pb-28 sm:px-6 md:px-8 xl:px-12 lg:max-w-6xl">
	<div class="py-16 sm:text-center">
		<h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl sm:text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold">Latest Posts</h1>
	</div>
<div class="relative sm:pb-12 sm:ml-[calc(2rem+1px)] md:ml-[calc(3.5rem+1px)] lg:ml-[max(calc(14.5rem+1px),calc(100%-48rem))]">
    <div class="hidden absolute top-3 bottom-0 right-full mr-7 md:mr-[3.25rem] w-px bg-base-200 dark:bg-base-800 sm:block"></div>
    <div class="space-y-16">
    	{% for p in site.posts limit:3 %}
    		{% include article-list.liquid %}
    	{% endfor %}
    </div>
</div>
	<div class="py-16 text-center">
		<a href="/blog" class="btn btn-primary btn-wide">View all posts</a>
	</div>
</div>